OL,3,CSculptor creates tiny golden dragon
OL,4,Csmaller than a matchstick for Lunar
OL,5,CNew Year
OL,7,FA renowned micro-sculptor has created
OL,8,Fa miniature golden dragon as "a symbol
OL,9,Fof strength" to celebrate the Lunar
OL,10,FNew Year.
OL,12,FWillard Wigan, from Birmingham, hand-
OL,13,Fcrafted a red-eyed dragon made from a
OL,14,Fsingle piece of gold smaller than the
OL,15,Fhead of a matchstick.
OL,17,FHe used microscopic hardened steel to
OL,18,Fshape the waves of the mystical
OL,19,Fcreature, and it took four months to
OL,20,Fcomplete.
