OL,3,CSculptor creates tiny golden dragon
OL,4,Csmaller than a matchstick for Lunar
OL,5,CNew Year
OL,7,F"I will never attempt that again
OL,8,Fbecause it was a nightmare to do," he
OL,9,Fexplained. "It took me four months of
OL,10,Fhard work trying to get it right
OL,11,Fbecause I failed a few times."
OL,13,FDespite disliking the process, he says
OL,14,Fhe finds enjoyment in creating pieces
OL,15,Fof art that people can admire.
OL,17,FHe said: "There was no pleasure in
OL,18,Fcreating this dragon. But the pleasure
OL,19,Fis when I finish it.
