OL,4,Csmaller than a matchstick for Lunar
OL,5,CNew Year
OL,7,FThe micro-sculptor said he did not use
OL,8,Fa reference picture to make the
OL,9,Fdragon, but instead used his
OL,10,Fphotographic memory of the mythical
OL,11,Fcreature to create an original design.
OL,13,FHe explained: "I started to cut the
OL,14,Fshape of the dragon out and this is
OL,15,Fnot using any photographs whatsoever.
OL,16,FThis is just me working from my mind."
