OL,3,CSculptor creates tiny golden dragon
OL,4,Csmaller than a matchstick for Lunar
OL,5,CNew Year
OL,7,FMr Wigan, who was made an MBE for
OL,8,Fservices to art in 2007, has been
OL,9,Fcreating microscopic sculptures since
OL,10,Fthe age of five when he began crafting
OL,11,Fhouses for ants.
OL,13,FBeing his most challenging piece to
OL,14,Fdate, he said he wanted to prove to
OL,15,Fhimself he could make the intricate
OL,16,Fcreation.
OL,18,F"I've got to the stage in my career
OL,19,Fwhen I thought, 'I'm nearly at my
OL,20,Fpeak, so I might as well attempt this
OL,21,Fdragon'," he said.
