OL,3,CSculptor creates tiny golden dragon
OL,4,Csmaller than a matchstick for Lunar
OL,5,CNew Year
OL,7,F"I was going to attempt it about four
OL,8,Fyears ago, but I thought no, I'm not
OL,9,Fready.
OL,11,F"I wanted to evolve to be at my peak
OL,12,Fto be able to do (the dragon) justice.
OL,13,FI wanted to prove to myself that I
OL,14,Fcould do it."
OL,16,FMr Wigan said the exclusive piece,
OL,17,Fwhich he described as "the best thing
OL,18,Fand the hardest thing I've ever done",
OL,19,Fwill be open to private viewings.
